_header: The debtor so is false and falling
_description: Qualities of Death — four lines — preceeded by Latin verson

BLHar7322.Transcription:
Þo dedtur so is fals and falendeStille and eke
                    stalkingeGredy and Crepyngesteorne and eke stellende
